Great service! I ordered a party box of sandwiches for our guys. The week was crazy busy and currently it is hard for them to get food on the go since we are not able to use drive through. From placing the order, to a call with friendly questions to the delivery early it was fantastic! Our team appreciated having something to grab between calls. The following day the manager called to ensure everything was what we wanted and that their service was up to par! Was so great to receive that call! In fact we ordered another party box the following day!

Franchise owner would not sell me a gift card without photo ID. Despite having the back of my mastercard signed and using a chip card with PIN, he would not process my payment. Claimed it was HIS policy and not Jimmy Johns' corporate. Refused to provide me with his name or a business card when I told him I would contact Corporate office. If you're going to turn away a $100 sale, you should at least be man enough to identify yourself. This location is in an upscale downtown apartment complex with $1500 one bedroom rentals, not some run down ghetto.
